<div style="background: #000; width: 100%; min-height: 180px;"><div style="color: #fff; width: 900px; margin: auto; padding: 4em 0; font-size: 9pt;">WARGuilds is a highly ambitious community website focusing on the upcoming release of Warhammer Online: Age of Reckoning. WARGuilds will be a one-stop shop for everything you need to learn, get involved with, and experience WAR at the highest level, completely free. <br /><br />You may be asking why FREE? Because after six years of playing MMOs, aren't you tired of IGN and its competitors? WARGuilds is a team of four dedicated players that have followed mythic since the early days of Dark Age of Camelot, and we're comitted to building the best possible WAR resource <em>ever</em>.<p>If you have webspace, bandwidth, servers, time or anything else that you'd like to contribute to the team; <a style="color: #fff;" href="mailto:admin@warhammerguilds.net?Subject=WARGuilds Team">We ARE Listening!</a></p></div></div>
